<h3 id="toc6"><span>Revision 4847/3RR0R updated <tt>985</tt> days ago</span></h3>
<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/shaggydredlocks-proposal/sun1.jpg" style="width:300px;" alt="sun1.jpg" class="image" />
