<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Did&nbsp;it&nbsp;have&nbsp;to&nbsp;end&nbsp;like&nbsp;that?</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<blockquote>
<p>You open the drawer, and pull out the gun. You absentmindedly turn it over in your hands for a moment, wondering where you'll go from here. Site-17? 64? Surely <a href="/umbra">you</a> can't be all that's <a href="/the-sun-ever-sets-on-the-british-empire">left</a>? The computer dings. There's been an update to the file?</p>
</blockquote>
